trial.&#148;</p>

<p ALIGN="LEFT">Yousuf opined that the most serious blunder the PA made was to adopt the
slogan &#147;Palestine for the Palestinians.&#148;</p>

<p ALIGN="LEFT">&#147;This enabled Israel to bully us and impose her will on us&#133;since
we can&#146;t alone stand up to Israeli hegemony and insolence.&#148; </p>

